item.title: Introduction to Data Wrangling, Analysis, & Communication
item.description: Part of a year-long curricula on open science, data, and research practice for incoming graduate students in the biomedical sciences, developed in collaboration with OHSU School of MedicineGraduate Studies. This course was offered at Oregon Health & Science University to graduate students in the biomedical sciences.
